{
  "stem": "20088.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they said, well, haven't you seen the crematorium burning?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, all those people have been gassed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You'll never see them again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was-- you know, they said it quite happily.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, it was cruel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- but one or two were quite kind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when somebody was nearly fainting, they said, don't faint.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Don't fall down, because you'll be right away selected.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Stand close to each other so that if you fall that you fall on somebody that the Germans wouldn't see that you faint.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the naked bodies kind of stuck together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were in shock.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was quite terrible, this first moment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we had to go in front of a table, all naked, and had to register our name, our profession, religion, everything.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And most people gave up professions which they didn't have.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my mother said, you are a seamstress.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at least you can do some work if they want to know what you can do.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I had no idea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that's what we did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother said something too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I don't know anymore what she said.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We all had professions.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- but all-- and exact birth, and date, and everything, quite long sheets.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that gave us hope, actually.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We thought, well, surely, they won't do all this if they are going-- intend to kill us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we had to go with our sheets of information in front to be tattooed our number, because from then on, though we had a name, it was all filed away then, the name with the number.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's why later, in a way, they could find information, because it was really all there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was typical Germans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They kept records, really, of everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, A5272.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
